cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.MM

The paper focuses on deep learning algorithms for classification tasks, specifically in the context of demographic attribute classification using image and text features. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Multimedia (cs.MM). Among these, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the paper's focus on deep learning algorithms for classification tasks using image and text features. The other categories are also relevant as they relate to the social media analysis and public health applications mentioned in the paper.
